{"tid":2370227,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"12種偏見 你中左幾多樣??","createTime":"2021-01-18T00:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T02:32:46.000Z","uid":246823,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8c0551c00f513a223579dbd0074586746d5e81","tid":2370227,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T00:26:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>1. Anchoring Bias</strong></span><br />\nCompletely relying on first informations<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D17&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=6ec6645a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=17</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>2. Availability Heuristic Bias</strong></span><br />\nOver estimating the importance of the available information<br />\n[/i]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D81&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=856b494d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=81</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>3. Bandwagon Effect</strong></span><br />\nBelieving something to be true because others do, i.e. following the rest without thinking<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D141&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=5549f686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=141</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>4. Choice Supportive Bias</strong></span><br />\n&quot;I made that choice so it must be right!!&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D188&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=fc0f0382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=188</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>5. Confirmation Bias</strong></span><br />\nA bias that makes us tend to listen the information that confirms what we already know<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D229&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=dfd8d1c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=229</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>6. Ostrich Bias</strong></span><br />\nDecision or subconscious decision to ignore negative information<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D269&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=a28fbccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=269</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>7. Outcome Bias</strong></span><br />\nJudging the efficacy of a decision primarily based on how things turn out<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D318&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=cd9c211a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=318</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>8. Overconfidence</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D371&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=4d673bb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=371</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>9. Placebo Bias</strong></span><br />\nBelieving something to have effect causes the effect<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D411&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=f808b32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=411</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>10. Surviving Bias</strong></span><br />\nJudging something based on surviving information<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D462&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=98e4850c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=462</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>11. Selective Perception</strong></span><br />\nA bias that causes you to perceive messages or actions according to your frame of reference<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D509&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=17e03451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=509</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>12. Blind Spot Bias</strong></span><br />\nWe are biased by thinking we are less biased than everyone else<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwEwGBIr_RIw%26t%3D546&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=d13af5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEwGBIr_RIw&amp;t=546</a>"},{"pid":"db8058b0afba598309046e6d91ec2387ef261945","tid":2370227,"uid":140599,"like":17,"dislike":13,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:23:24.000Z","msg":"內文全部英文 唔該你標題用返英文pls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fc129f59b4605c9b65c383b365e9022966080f","tid":2370227,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"想睇字"},{"pid":"0875a7fd2f79bedb6aabba7b1890f62d1ada1243","tid":2370227,"uid":113250,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:37:29.000Z","msg":"連登個UI應該會導致比較多人中Anchoring Bias，愈碌到下面就愈多information要處理，所以出於人嘅惰性，會比較傾向同意頭嘅comment."},{"pid":"d38ff27a7e82d2a05a804409b7600baa06cd4924","tid":2370227,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8058b0afba598309046e6d91ec2387ef261945","tid":2370227,"uid":140599,"like":17,"dislike":13,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:23:24.000Z","msg":"內文全部英文 唔該你標題用返英文pls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"應該好快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120f18c6bf44be29e337da803470df393869f7c3","tid":2370227,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187828ff78ee1a1b239aa6a1d8f62af0aefc8e9d","tid":2370227,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddf391d914b40018b243fa4fb6f820917cc2b23","tid":2370227,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0